Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}尤托利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了 这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}找到大案子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大案子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起大案子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:02:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}烤乳猪啦海鲜魔兽井啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是大盘子啊  姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我当然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以大案子是指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只要找到宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}应该就能支付遗产税了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真是件大事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过这是哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}朋友让给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是我找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我叫玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}可爱的天才魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}自称天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}看起来也就10多岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}年纪这么小态度还这么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你刚刚在想我年纪很小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还觉得我很嚣张对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我才没这那么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真敏锐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我以前在某个委托中认识了玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}他很了解魔法知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}甚至还跳级从冒险者专门学校毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那还真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}叫我玛莉卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}跪下舔我的脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}性格上倒是有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以这张地图是你找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一起找到宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家分了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}赶紧动身去寻宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}寻宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来以前也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我最喜欢这种活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们接下来有重要的事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有做劲倒是挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是可没时间等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}给人捷足先登就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}绝对要替我找到宝藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也无法保证啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是个支付遗产税
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}拿回遗产的好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}无论如何 不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}都要找到宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}压力好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这社长光看就不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}都让小孩子担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也会一起去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}而且社长他关键时刻很可靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大概
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就连青梅竹马秘书都这么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我一定会拿回宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家就期待我回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}该从哪里开始找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}首先是 在绿之迷宫挖掘鹿角的地面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}绿之迷宫在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}难道是在城镇郊外的鲁鲁多森林吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那边出了名的容易迷路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说不定真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不知道正不正确就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}虽然不太可信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}总之先去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}总是会带句多余的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}什么 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}全部卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}限定商品总是特别抢手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}亏我为了这一天存好了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还想着要大买特买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}特地带弟弟一起来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}姊姊意外地喜欢可爱的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}早知如此就该一起去寻宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只让社长跟尤托利亚两个人去 放不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长跟尤托利亚小姐是什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是听说前社长收养并照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}无家可归的尤托利亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}听说他们小时候就跟兄妹一般相处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}刚刚也想提起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们小时候也常常一起寻宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一起探索办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}找到藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}尤托利亚还说不找到宝藏不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}结果寻宝到天都黑了才回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那天爸爸可生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}结果还是没找到宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那张地图到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}别在那边秀恩爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}秀恩爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎样都好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这里就是鲁鲁多森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}郁郁苍苍繁密的树林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真的就像迷宫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过鹿角又是指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}会不会在某处插着根鹿角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这张地图是在哪找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在冒险者爷爷家里的仓库发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那问问你爷爷不就能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}问不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}他一年前过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}都活到120岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也算是善终了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}赶紧去找鹿角了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过  瞎找也不是办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大哥哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我会付钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}汤玛士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有好好把礼物送给姊姊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}姊姊可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大哥哥来这边做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}汤玛士  你知不知道鹿角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这附近人人知晓的景点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是指这前方的两颗树啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不嫌麻烦的话可以带个路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}要依赖这个小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}叫我小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你几岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那么我比你大2岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}叫我玛莉卡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不要使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这家伙真凶暴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}总之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}能拜托你带路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一个个都不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}靠这群人真能找到宝藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有宝物啊姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你说这根香菇是宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不能摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这味道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那株 曲鼻菇 有着强烈的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一摸到没个三天气味是不会散的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这东西哪里宝物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过这香菇很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是梦幻香菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还超级好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}虽然要捏着鼻子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}捏着鼻子还尝的出味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这里就是鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}的确像是鹿角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还没找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等一下  我正在挖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这里真的是鹿角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就说了是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这座森林里我只想的到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}挖到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是宝藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快点  快点拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}比想像中小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}里面是不是装宝石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不要故弄玄虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快点打开他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是  纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}写着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}调查鬼屋深处的画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是告诉我们下一步的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说不定只是碰巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}要不是有汤玛士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们可就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}别客气别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}小事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这场寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}能不能算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}感觉很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我很有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就是这样我才讨厌小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等一下啊汤玛士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}接下来要 调查鬼屋深处的画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但我完全没有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那一定是附近的废屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}附近的小孩都称他为鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有预想到应该价格不斐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但没想到竟然这么贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}才不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我的手有够臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我有带个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}导航小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么突然出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是特殊技能 暗隐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}碰巧看见两位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就想要吓吓你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}来  请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不管什么恶臭都能一举消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}鬼印的消臭喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}导航小姐不是跟社长一起去寻宝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}突然有紧急的汇款作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}而且我也不想打扰社长 和尤托利亚的回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我在 希望 任职也很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}知道很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}导航小姐也是浑身谜团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}希望你尽量不要在城里用特殊技能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这里就是鬼屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就是这间废屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}原来这边有间废屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}会在这附近玩的人基本上都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡住哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}叫我玛莉卡姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我就住在那边的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不就在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但却完全没来过废屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}管我那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡没朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}看你这反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}果然没猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我不需要什么朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}孤僻的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}两位关系变得相当好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玩的开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就凭着这股劲直接发现宝藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}眼神有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这里就是鬼屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没有人烟一片漆黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}前进时当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还好吗 尤托利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样可不能好好前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真是毫无作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}亮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是点灯魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样就能前进了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}法杖发光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}让我摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等  别摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过  玛莉卡还真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}现在才知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以就叫我玛莉卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡要成为冒险者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在我懂事时就志愿成为冒险者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}爷爷他是伟大的魔法师受人尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}而我想承继他的衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}看来是个好爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我最喜欢爷爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么弯过来就是道墙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还上着锁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过看来只有这边有路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}要破门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就这样撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}太粗暴的话有可能整栋建筑物垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}的确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这边有个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我钻过去开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过对面黑漆漆的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那么这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢  汤玛士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有两位在真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我可是天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}再多感谢我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}非常感谢两位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}步调都被打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快点走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长和尤托利亚从小就一起寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也是从前社长听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}两人拼尽全力  同心协力寻找宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}正好跟那位玛莉卡差不多年纪的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}再一下下就到最深处了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊  要好好跟上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一路到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}简直像是为那两人量身打造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来还真有这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}应该只是巧合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快去寻宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}已经没有路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那么这边就是最深处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这张纸条写着 调查鬼屋深处的画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是指那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等一下 有什么在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这种地方竟然有魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}城镇周边应该不会出现魔兽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}果然  说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}事到如今只能一战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}汤玛士和玛莉卡先退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}本玛莉卡大人来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一击就打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}幽灵类的魔兽最怕火属性魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}魔法还真帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样就排除危险了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}来去确认目标画作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有东西在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是 信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}信 那就是宝藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了 尤托利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这封信写着 致亲爱的玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}为什么写着我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}致亲爱的玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你读这封信的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}想必我已经不在人世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我活得够久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}人生已无眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过尚有一件挂心事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那就是你  玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你从小就聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}或许也因如此 身旁总是我这般的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}完全没有同龄的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}爷爷 我出门了 当然 你说要继承我的衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这非常令人开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是也担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是否会因此更难交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以我留下了藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡只身一人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}终究无法寻获这份宝藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡的魔法 邻近小孩的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我设计成只有集合这两者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}才能够找到这份宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}愿你能找到无可估量的  真正的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}致我珍贵的玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这都是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我才不需要什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只要爷爷陪着我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你爷爷也希望你交个朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那又怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那不就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我已经是玛莉卡的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是朋友了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}嚣张什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我就说我不需要朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过我们已经是朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}请多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}叫我玛莉卡姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}太好了呢  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}虽然没有找到宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是胸口暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不管什么时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}寻宝一类的活动 总能拉近小孩子的距离呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}难不成那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们小时候一起去寻宝了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那时尤托利亚刚来我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来那时我们两个还很生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是不是爸爸想让我们好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}故意放了藏宝图呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就像玛莉卡的爷爷那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}如果是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那还真是得好好感谢前社长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}多亏了他我们才打好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}虽然他还骂我们回家晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那点也很像前社长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}无法估量的  真正的宝物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一定就是指朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:21:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}宝物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}应该有找到值钱货吧

